              "text": "Guided Test Case Generation through AI Enabled Output Space Exploration",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/AST2018-6u6Liga3r6oE8Zrz9Cs4GC/11hhr7CPNnfYaW9qEmygP0/32ohC2qOtGOIBI9PYVHIuz.pdf",
