              "text": "Towards Gender Equality in Software Engineering: The NSA Approach",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/GE2018-5lsO9wN3fGslwPufsqk9fU/1KJndBaazISxVniTHCt7kc/7j1XH2EzmBNkihiz6XLDhk.pdf",
