              "type": "authorPaper",
              "text": "Predictive Analytics for Software Testing",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/SBST2018-77UFPTELICBMLdRdBsqxwb/6kO4Mp3Y1rSfHM8mu5y2QL/4FB8IQ0w7Z2lvfU7R2Craj.pdf",
              "extraLocations": [],
              "authorNames": "Federica Sarro (University College London)",
              "abstract": "This keynote discusses the use of Predictive Analytics for Software Engineering, and in particular for Software Defect Prediction and Software Testing, by presenting the latest results achieved in these fields leveraging Artificial Intelligence, Search-based and Machine Learning methods, and by giving some directions for future work.",
              "searchText": "2018 ACM/IEEE 11th International Workshop on Search-Based Software Testing SBST 2018 Predictive Analytics for Software Testing 1521729329448 Federica Sarro University College London f.sarro@ucl.ac.uk Predictive Analytics Search-based Predictive Modelling This keynote discusses the use of Predictive Analytics for Software Engineering, and in particular for Software Defect Prediction and Software Testing, by presenting the latest results achieved in these fields leveraging Artificial Intelligence, Search-based and Machine Learning methods, and by giving some directions for future work.",
