              "text": "On Using Blockchains for Safety-Critical Systems",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/SEsCPS2018-5Ys6vFczJb8vtJTIC0U1kP/54YrxJ7n6jPS84ujmz1VIM/5jn8NZXdNP6CdYcEXF2Hy0.pdf",
