              "text": "Software Quality through the Eyes of the End-User and Static Analysis Tools: A Study on Android OSS Applications",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/SQUADE2018-52YkchboRqqdpLhjNfFOjE/7hqeAUT4YI9YF89kIYJicD/5R84ZWjecBQFdmGptJ53nb.pdf",
