              "text": "SHARVOT: Secret SHARe-Based VOTing on the Blockchain",
              "articleLocation": "pdfs/WETSEB2018-4yg6Vlc41C9KIaprNBrkzl/2uG92sL03I9nPKCFr7XITM/5irjL6lITwZJ9RLJArjADV.pdf",
